number of agreements to enhance bilateral cooperation and
institutionalize the regular consultations between the two
countries, according to the Prime Minister.
</P>
<P>
While in Belgium, Sharif will hold discussions with the Belgium
leadership on bilateral, regional and international matters of
mutual interest.
</P>
<P>
